= Pastiche

== Description

Simple pastebin application using Sinatra with OpenID authentication.

== Install

Edit +config.ru+ and run +rackup+.

Required libraries are:

- Sinatra
- Haml
- Ruby OpenID
- DataMapper
- Ultraviolet

Required libraries for development are:

- RSpec
- Webrat
- Rack-Test

